<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n04164h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n04" href="#n04164h">N04 (VI.B.25)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n04all.htm#n04164h"> 164(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> the Luna ball / (inflate &amp; deflate)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Deptford Woman Awarded &pound;1000 Damages</b> Miss Kathleen Sheehan, of Deptford, who claimed damages for injuries sustained while riding on the Luna Ball at Dreamland Park, Margate, was to-day awarded &pound;1000 and costs by Mr. Justice Avory in the King&apos;s Bench Division against Dreamland (Margate) Ltd. <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> The <mark>Luna Ball</mark> was a sixpenny sideshow, and the amusement consisted of riding on a large ball which was <mark>inflated and deflated</mark>. <small> <a name="ES27jul23" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ES27jul23"><cite title="source">Evening Standard</cite></a> (27 July 1923) 7/2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
